profile_positions.description:
Main Responsibilities: 
- Full life cycle of IT recruiting (Main Roles: DevOps, Data Scientist and Software Engineer); 
- Develop and implement new sourcing strategies;  
- Hiring and Onboarding more than 40 employees for the 3 core business areas; 
- Responsible for the relationship with Universities;  
- Organize and Planning Events (e.g. Career fairs, Tech festivals); 
- Onboarding, coaching and coordinating  4 new elements of the HR team;  
- Implement a new ATS; 
- Salary and benefits analysis for the Portuguese Market; 
- HR Surveys (Recruitment & Onboarding and Employee Culture & Satisfaction for US and PT);
